        value=0)
```
Finds those two paths as well as others.

However,
```python
contract_account.test(
        m.make_symbolic_buffer(32),
        m.make_symbolic_buffer(32),
        m.make_symbolic_buffer(32),
        m.make_symbolic_buffer(32),
        caller=owner_account)
```
only finds the REVERT path.
Similarly for,
```python
contract_account.test(
        m.make_symbolic_buffer(320),
        caller=owner_account)
```

